WEBVTT

00:00.068 --> 00:01.767
<i>Previously on The Whispers...</i>

00:01.803 --> 00:03.630
Lena: Drill, I want you
to leave my daughter alone.

00:03.771 --> 00:05.137
I'll do whatever it takes.

00:05.172 --> 00:06.838
Drill said he wants something from you.

00:06.874 --> 00:08.407
Maybe you can make a deal.

00:08.442 --> 00:11.143
I lived with this thing in
my head for three months.

00:11.178 --> 00:13.645
- What <i> does</i> it want?
- To destroy us, sir.

00:13.680 --> 00:16.581
- [Electricity crackles]
- It's Drill. He's here.

00:16.617 --> 00:19.918
Wes, we can end this,
get rid of Drill for good.

00:19.953 --> 00:22.454
[Explosion]

00:22.489 --> 00:24.289
Take my car. You run. Go.

00:24.324 --> 00:25.957
Claire Bennigan was responsible.

00:25.993 --> 00:28.927
Bennigan's son... I
want him in our custody.

00:36.503 --> 00:40.739
Are you sure my mom's gonna be there?

00:40.774 --> 00:45.410
Don't worry, Henry. It
should be just up ahead.

00:47.000 --> 00:53.074
